nd all there points on str and sta and even then i got higher str plus regen and i pulled off getting to ten in 7 hours NOT TWINKED just because innothule and guk gators plus the newbie quest 2 tadpole fleshes and 1 froggy neat gives you rusty 2 handed axe in case you want to train that not to mention on Rallos Zek Ive never been defeated or pked is what they call it even at 2 bubbles of life except once but i was 5 and he 10 and twinked.</p>&nbsp;<br> </td></td></tr>
